{"tid":2100868,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"屌你老味！仲用中資銀行做按揭，即係幫維尼回血！","createTime":"2020-07-09T10:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T13:16:01.000Z","uid":90735,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51c883bbacfecccbb98838c3fb0330e04c3248f2","tid":2100868,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:48:55.000Z","msg":"房屋台仲gogogo緊<br />\n時事台手足可能wfc，但按揭服務係金融戰重要一環<br />\n所以開post提下大家<br />\n<br />\nAnyway<br />\n如果你本身有樓，又用緊中資銀行做按揭<br />\n你有冇諗過即係<span class=\"red\">每年俾差唔多7-10幾萬利息俾維尼回血</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要，懺悔時間到<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一係轉按、一係賣樓</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>轉按</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定義：之前買完樓，按揭過咗罰息期，你可以轉去其他銀行做按揭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解轉按：賺銀行回贈(幾皮)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 程序：同新做按揭差唔多，要過壓測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>搞按揭搵轉介，銀行按揭部自動打俾你</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 填完按揭轉介form之後，agent會幫你搵銀行，銀行會自動聯絡你傾rate ，唔洗自己打俾銀行咁煩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> agent 成功refer 只收銀行中介費，唔會收你錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記得叫agent 指明要搵某啲銀行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵邊間轉介？自己google「按揭轉介」，唔好意思，費事俾人話我係按揭打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6e6018dc5d271d89764157b5d7322f638d19df","tid":2100868,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66622a85a341d5de5f138e0d28c3cb3c549c38af","tid":2100868,"